collections.description:
#I'm Frank.
10,000 unique NFTs created by YourFaceHere and NFTBoom.

Full Road Map available on the Website and in our Discord.

ALL offers at floor or above it will be considered. Any questions, please don't hesitate to ask. We are available on Instagram, Twitter, imfrank.uk and of course our discord.

Because we're all a little bit Frank.
collections.name: I'm Frank

collections.description:
What better way to show your nearest and dearest how much you care than with a unique flower.

Each flower is unique and will never be re-minted so you can guarantee yours is truly special.

 Designed, individually hand re-coloured and re-rendered by G.B. (YourFaceHere).

There are Currently 2 series, with each series containing 20 Flowers. Also I'll be adding "one off special editions" over time.

If you have any requests or questions please don't hesitate to contact me. Also please visit nftboom.co.uk where you can find out a little more about the history of this design and you can also verify that your flower is a YourFaceHere original.
